      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VrS82.28 (mss. 2005, 2007, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2101, 2104, 2106, 2109, 4000, 4010, 4020, 4050, 4055, 4161, 4162, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em> dō guftan ud pad harw <em>š́iiaōθənanąm</em> rāspīg ēsm ud bōy nihādag ō ī ātaxš dādan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "He should recite twice the <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em>. At each <em>š́iiaōθənanąm</em>, (the <em>rāspīg</em>) should give to the fire the <em>ēsm</em> and <em>bōy</em>
            that have been prepared previously."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
